

<div class="container-fluid m-0 p-0">
    <div class="privacy-content p-5" style="height: 100vh; overflow-y: auto;  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);">

        @{
            ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
        }
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.</p>

        <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Such as name, email address, phone number, etc. when you fill out forms or register.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on pages, browser type, IP address, and other analytics data.</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies and Tracking:</strong> We use cookies to enhance user experience and analyze website traffic.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide, operate, and maintain our services.</li>
            <li>To improve, personalize, and expand our website.</li>
            <li>To understand and analyze how you use our website.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>3. Sharing Your Information</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties.</li>
            <li>We may share information with service providers who perform services on our behalf.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-muted">Use this page to detail your site's privacy policy.</p>
    </div>
</div>


